<li>Chad Orzel (2019/04/25), “<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/chadorzel/2019/04/25/neutrino-physics-and-a-history-of-impossible-experiments/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Neutrino Physics And A History Of Impossible Experiments</a>“, Forbes.</li>
<li>S.M. Bilenkya (2013), “Neutrino. History of a unique particle", Eur. Phys. J. H 38, 345–404.</li>
